---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Base
  title="JoyTap Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for JoyTap, a sensory play app for toddlers."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-12 font-mono">
    <section class="mb-12 fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-6">joytap privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-foreground/60 mb-8">last updated: march 12, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground/80">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">summary</h2>
          <p>JoyTap collects no personal data. No accounts, no tracking, no analytics, no ads. It's a sensory play app for toddlers, built for one family.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">data collection</h2>
          <p>JoyTap does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. The app runs entirely on your device with no network requests.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">local storage</h2>
          <p>The app stores a single preference (sound on/off) using the device's local storage. This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to anyone else.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">third-party services</h2>
          <p>JoyTap uses no third-party SDKs, analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">children's privacy</h2>
          <p>JoyTap is designed for use by toddlers under parental supervision. The app does not collect any information from children or anyone else.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this policy? Reach out via the <a href="/contact" class="underline hover:no-underline">contact page</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
